---

<Layout>
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="avatar-section">
                <div class="avatar-placeholder">
                    <span class="avatar-initials">LE</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-section">
                <div class="bio-text">
                    <p>
                        I’m a software engineer and engineering manager with a
                        broad, polyglot background and a strong T-shaped
                        approach to building and leading. I care about clear
                        thinking, solid architecture, and helping teams ship
                        meaningful work without creating unnecessary complexity.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I’m especially interested in what an AI-first, agentic
                        future means for engineering. I enjoy experimenting with
                        AI in real workflows, shaping practical guardrails for
                        teams, and exploring how our roles evolve as automation
                        becomes part of everyday development. Outside of work,
                        I’m an indie builder and tinkerer, constantly
                        prototyping new ideas and learning.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="social-links">
                    {
                        socialLinks.map((link) => (
                            <a
                                href={link.url}
                                aria-label={link.name}
                                class="social-link"
                                set:html={link.icon}
                            />
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header-section {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .content-wrapper {
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 3rem;
        }
    }

    .avatar-section {
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .avatar-placeholder {
        width: 160px;
        height: 160px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: var(--color-border);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .avatar-initials {
        font-family: var(--font-family-display);
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .text-section {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .bio-text {
        font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .bio-text p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .bio-text p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .social-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        background-color: transparent;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
        color: var(--color-bg);
        background-color: var(--color-text);
        border-color: var(--color-text);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    :global(.social-link svg) {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
    }
</style>
